songs.title: THEY SUSPENDED MY TWITTER
songs.lyrics:
[Intro: SmokePurpp & Lil Pump]
Aye man
Hatin' ass niggas got my nigga Lil Pump twitter deleted, nigga
But we don't give a fuck nigga
He got a new Twitter
New Twitter, new-
Hell yeah man
Fuck all y'all hatin' ass niggas man
SmokePurpp, Lil Pump, in this bitch, man
Damn son, where'd you find this?
Aye, aye

[Chorus: Lil Pump & SmokePurpp]
They suspended my twitter, aye
They suspended my twitter, aye
They suspended my twitter, aye, (what?)
They suspended my twitter, aye, (what?)
But I got a new twitter, aye
But I got a new twitter, aye
But I got a new twitter, aye
They suspended my twitter, aye, (what?)
They suspended my twitter, aye
They suspended my twitter, aye
They suspended my twitter, what
They suspended my twitter, what
